  • Classes in it.polimi.deib.se2019.sanp4.adrenaline.common.requests used by it.polimi.deib.se2019.sanp4.adrenaline.client 
    Class and Description
    ChoiceRequest
    An abstract class representing a request to choose between various alternatives, made to a player.
    ChoiceRequestVisitor
    An interface describing an object using the visitor pattern to handle choice requests Classes implementing this interface are encouraged to handle all types of requests.
